lead_paragraph: Saudi Arabia will send four women to the Rio de Janeiro Olympics, doubling its female participation after two women competed for the first time at the 2012 London Games.

headline.print_headline: Saudi Arabia Doubles Female Olympic Athletes From 2 to 4
